text: Bangalaia ochreomarmorata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1958. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia ochreomarmorata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1958
